subtitleeditor: subtitleeditor (GTK+ Subtitle Editor)
subtitleeditor:
subtitleeditor: Subtitle Editor is a GTK+2 tool to edit subtitles for GNU/Linux/*BSD.
subtitleeditor: It can be used for new subtitles or as a tool to transform, edit,
subtitleeditor: correct and refine existing subtitle. This program also shows sound
subtitleeditor: waves, which makes it easier to synchronise subtitles to voices.
subtitleeditor: Subtitle Editor is free software released under the GPL version 3.
subtitleeditor:
subtitleeditor: URL: http://home.gna.org/subtitleeditor/
